# CLIP Basics

## What is CLIP?

CLIP (Contrastive Language Image Pre-training) is a multimodal AI model developed by OpenAI.

It learns the relationship between images and text by mapping both into a shared embedding space.

## Architecture

Image
→ Image Encoder
→ Image Embedding

Text
→ Text Encoder
→ Text Embedding

Similarity between embeddings helps determine whether an image and text match.

## Key Concepts

- Image Encoder
- Text Encoder
- Embeddings
- Cosine Similarity
- Contrastive Learning

## Applications

- Image Search
- Product Recommendation
- Multimodal Retrieval
- Visual Question Answering

